description: Say goodbye to endlessly circling the block—this deeded parking spot offers the ultimate convenience in one of Southie's most sought-after neighborhoods. Located in a boutique condo building at the corner of L Street and East 3rd, this heated garage space provides year-round comfort and peace of mind.It’s more than just parking—it’s a smart investment. Just three blocks away, the highly anticipated redevelopment of the Edison Power Plant is set to transform the area with 636 new housing units and 1.7 million square feet of office and retail space.As the neighborhood grows, so will the value of this prime parking spot. Enjoy the convenience of no more parking tickets, no more shoveling, and no more stress—just pull in and relax. Currently rented month to month for $450/mo.
